{"tid":1471682,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"發夢發到好無能為力...","createTime":"2019-08-14T10:34:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T09:46:33.000Z","uid":271614,"like":17,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":44,"replies":[{"pid":"d7dfa31546069c7f0b85f83d049a81cfa230f637","tid":1471682,"uid":271614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T10:34:43.000Z","msg":"小弟本身只係個Cdrom好少上黎打野<br />\n但經過811-813呢幾日開始覺得頂唔順啦...<br />\n見到ig,fb,lihkg都係講緊呢兩個月既野 不斷係到loop <br />\n721 811我都有發夢 個種痛心 我同大家都一樣<br />\n作為發夢既一份子 親眼睇住手足比人禁住拉<br />\n但又淆底唔夠薑去拉番作地 個種無力感...<br />\n作為學生 更加無力係因為每一次發夢都用好多錢 <br />\n但最後慢慢睇住自己pt 儲落啲錢係户口慢慢咁減少 <br />\n去到個位數字.. 呢種感覺更加無力.. 覺得自己好無用...<br />\n所以先係到發洩下.. 1999唔好意思.."},{"pid":"0906bd9fd61d63d4d10c385ee0b43f7203387082","tid":1471682,"uid":271614,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T10:38:08.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae7fe5ef3cd3c7e58c65cdb073247fece89cbe41","tid":1471682,"uid":271614,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T10:41:44.000Z","msg":"有冇人可以開解下我.."},{"pid":"9949b90cb2abbbe315cb70741106e9f7ad1a9ea0","tid":1471682,"uid":271614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T10:53:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />係咪要單機啦"},{"pid":"6b4f4434301ad2bfa0a3a4b1a6889262e035da5b","tid":1471682,"uid":271614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T10:59:43.000Z","msg":"係咪開錯台..."},{"pid":"98cad9dbd34cf964f473373f71bb27ab7502743d","tid":1471682,"uid":5327,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T11:04:22.000Z","msg":"需要食餐飯嘅可以講，第一時間趕到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cafb48a67156b27521a4ed3733c761cdd88e0